WEBVTT

01:57.970 --> 01:59.730
Give up. Give up, I said.

02:01.300 --> 02:02.590
Get out of my face.

02:06.390 --> 02:08.080
Move it. Move it.

02:09.389 --> 02:10.720
Fuck you up!

02:15.150 --> 02:16.820
Break it up!

02:34.740 --> 02:36.500
Come on, back off.
Take your hands off me.

02:52.980 --> 02:54.070
Take this, take this!

03:12.830 --> 03:14.620
Tell me, Twitch.

03:15.510 --> 03:17.540
- Who started this?
- My name's Twitch...

03:17.660 --> 03:21.190
...and I ain't no snitch.
I don't know nothing, man.

03:21.690 --> 03:23.350
You're worried?

03:23.830 --> 03:25.630
About them?

03:26.940 --> 03:29.170
What they could do to you?

03:29.880 --> 03:31.980
You should worry more about me.

03:32.090 --> 03:35.760
- And what I'm gonna do to you.
- Look, man, I'm just working.

03:35.810 --> 03:37.670
Just doing my time.

03:37.790 --> 03:39.920
Just doing my time.

03:41.410 --> 03:43.840
Model citizen.

03:44.610 --> 03:47.510
See, Twitch has been here
a long time...

03:47.580 --> 03:49.740
...seen lot of shit go down.

03:49.850 --> 03:53.050
Like inmates trying to take over.

03:53.120 --> 03:56.780
But I slapped them down
like little bitches.

03:56.830 --> 03:59.920
Nobody wins in my island...

04:00.000 --> 04:01.300
...but me.

04:03.870 --> 04:06.600
What do you think, homeys?

04:06.690 --> 04:10.050
Should I put any of you in the hole?

04:10.110 --> 04:11.940
Shit.

04:12.070 --> 04:14.900
Lot of guys like you in the hole...

04:14.980 --> 04:17.570
...guys who think they're tough...

04:18.269 --> 04:21.670
...guys who are beginning
to believe...

04:21.730 --> 04:24.360
...they're bigger...

04:24.450 --> 04:26.650
...than my island.

04:32.290 --> 04:34.520
You bay beauties...

04:34.630 --> 04:38.060
...you don't know
how fucking good you got it.

04:38.120 --> 04:39.580
Hey...

04:39.720 --> 04:41.410
...bag of bones.

04:41.990 --> 04:45.430
You wouldn't last two weeks
in a place like Creighton.

04:45.480 --> 04:47.270
- Toughest max- security joint...
- Creigh- -?

04:47.400 --> 04:49.330
...in the country.

04:49.800 --> 04:52.060
In case you never heard of it.

04:52.870 --> 04:55.170
It's where society took a shit.

04:55.270 --> 04:58.670
And built a 40- foot wall around it.

04:58.730 --> 05:02.390
And any of you could end up there...

05:02.440 --> 05:05.430
...with a snap of my fingers.

05:06.180 --> 05:07.980
So...

05:08.100 --> 05:11.040
...everybody's on notice.

05:11.110 --> 05:13.910
Whoever starts the next fight...

05:14.570 --> 05:19.440
...gets a free ride, no questions asked,
to Creighton.

05:19.430 --> 05:25.130
Then you can see
how bad you really are.

05:26.380 --> 05:28.400
Now, get them back to their cages.

05:28.520 --> 05:30.790
They're starting to give me
indigestion.

05:34.600 --> 05:36.970
Come on, line it up and let's move.

05:38.190 --> 05:40.490
Lock your chains. Let's go.

05:40.590 --> 05:43.560
- That means you too.
- Back it up.

05:43.630 --> 05:45.650
Creighton, huh?
That's in Missouri, ain't it?

06:01.070 --> 06:02.660
Hey, Twitch.

06:02.800 --> 06:05.030
Heard you got deep- sixed
at your parole hearing.

06:05.130 --> 06:08.130
Looks like you're not getting out
anytime soon.

06:08.210 --> 06:10.510
Oh, fuck you, Hubert.

06:10.610 --> 06:13.940
I'm out in a month.
Mark it on your calendar.

06:14.000 --> 06:16.470
While you rot in here, I get the gold.

06:16.560 --> 06:18.690
Yeah, I'll be out a lot sooner
than you think.

06:18.800 --> 06:21.400
Oh, yeah? You gonna dog paddle
off this rock?

06:21.490 --> 06:25.590
- Oh, I got ways.
- A month, Twitch. That's what I got.

06:25.620 --> 06:28.590
Yeah? And I got a nice,
stern ass- whupping for you...

06:28.660 --> 06:31.460
...if you don't leave me
the fuck alone.

06:38.390 --> 06:39.950
You.

06:40.310 --> 06:42.100
You're gonna move, man?
Wanna move a play?

06:42.230 --> 06:43.490
No.

06:44.440 --> 06:45.730
Shit.

06:45.880 --> 06:48.000
Perfect.

06:48.920 --> 06:51.750
Hey. What's up, motherfucker?

06:51.830 --> 06:54.800
- I'm talking to you, motherfucker.
- What do you want, Twitch?

06:54.870 --> 06:56.890
I wanna kick your ass.

06:57.010 --> 07:00.180
- Man, come on, get your ass up.
- You can't be serious.

07:00.250 --> 07:02.650
Nigga, you've been talking shit
about me.

07:02.740 --> 07:03.900
When? What proof you got?

07:04.050 --> 07:06.890
I don't need no proof.
Man, you sound like a lawyer.

07:06.970 --> 07:09.130
How can you see with these
motherfuckers on here- -

07:09.240 --> 07:11.230
- Give them back.
- Fuck, no.

07:11.350 --> 07:15.080
Why don't you come get them from me
so I could kick your ass?

07:15.130 --> 07:16.460
You know I'm out in a month.

07:16.600 --> 07:18.830
- I'm not gonna fight you.
- Damn.

07:20.380 --> 07:23.440
- But my bitch will.
- What bitch?

07:24.920 --> 07:27.860
Oh, shit. Okay.
Here. Hey, you gotta- -

07:33.210 --> 07:34.730
Come here.

07:35.230 --> 07:36.850
- Fuck, yeah.
- Oh, shit.

07:48.000 --> 07:50.020
Get up and walk.
Get up and walk.

07:50.140 --> 07:52.470
- What was that?
- Easy, easy.

07:52.570 --> 07:54.370
- Get up.
- I'll kick your ass.

07:54.490 --> 07:57.720
You make sure you tell the warden
that I started this, you hear me?

07:57.790 --> 08:01.090
You hear me? You tell- -  What the fuck
are you- -? I'll kick your ass too.

08:24.830 --> 08:28.170
Good morning, gentlemen.
Welcome to Creighton.

08:29.410 --> 08:33.240
My name is Mr. Wallace,
and I'm the warden of this prison.

08:33.280 --> 08:36.340
I wanted to personally greet you
by saying:

08:36.419 --> 08:38.549
I run a tight ship.

08:38.659 --> 08:41.530
My prison, my rules.

08:41.990 --> 08:46.250
Best advice I can give to you
is keep to yourself...

08:46.280 --> 08:49.180
...do your time
and don't break my rules.

08:49.250 --> 08:51.020
No matter how tough
you think you are- -

08:51.140 --> 08:53.970
And I know some of you think
you're real tough.

08:54.690 --> 08:56.750
- - I will break you.

08:57.090 --> 08:58.890
That's a promise.

08:59.010 --> 09:00.810
Understood?

09:00.930 --> 09:03.960
I got your back. I'm with you.

09:09.670 --> 09:10.830
Step forward.

09:14.790 --> 09:16.920
Listen up, punk.

09:17.030 --> 09:21.700
I know you like to cause problems.
That's why you got sent here.

09:21.700 --> 09:26.840
I'm gonna personally see to it
that that doesn't happen anymore.

09:26.830 --> 09:31.190
My officers will resort
to any and all measures necessary...

09:31.210 --> 09:33.040
...to keep you in line.

09:33.160 --> 09:34.930
Understand?

09:35.400 --> 09:37.160
Whatever you say, man. I'm not- -

09:37.290 --> 09:38.990
You'll keep your nose clean...

09:39.110 --> 09:42.380
...and stay out of other people's
affairs, won't you?

09:42.760 --> 09:46.060
Hey, man, look. You know,
I only concentrate on my own- -

09:48.360 --> 09:51.800
I'm not sure
I really heard you correctly.

09:51.850 --> 09:55.020
I just want to do my time and leave.

09:55.080 --> 09:57.380
That's what I thought you said.

09:58.320 --> 10:00.440
I'll remember you.

10:08.110 --> 10:12.140
Pick up your prison blues
and your shoes.

10:12.180 --> 10:14.270
Show them to their cellblocks.

10:14.670 --> 10:16.830
- Here you go.
- Next.

10:16.940 --> 10:19.710
- Here you go.
- Next.

10:20.050 --> 10:21.020
Here you go.

10:21.170 --> 10:23.830
Where you got your soap, kid?

10:23.920 --> 10:27.450
Shake my hand.
Come on. Shake my hand.

10:44.920 --> 10:46.380
This shit they call food- -

10:46.520 --> 10:47.950
Keep your eyes on the room.

10:48.080 --> 10:51.210
- Copy that.
- Anything could be a diversion.

10:54.960 --> 10:58.920
Only take one second for these
bastards to start killing each other.

10:59.450 --> 11:02.710
Sometimes I wonder why we bother
standing in the way.

11:12.410 --> 11:15.000
How long I gotta wait
in line to get food?

11:51.040 --> 11:52.260
What's up with that?

11:52.410 --> 11:55.680
Baboso wants more money
for bringing in the piece.

11:55.740 --> 11:58.070
Mira, you know
how much that mule was paid?

11:58.170 --> 12:00.110
Let me just cut him a piece.

12:05.730 --> 12:07.850
What if this motherfucker's
double- dealing...

12:07.970 --> 12:09.360
...with the Disciples, homes?

12:09.500 --> 12:12.130
- Let me do this.
- Are you sure?

12:31.910 --> 12:33.570
You shouldn't be sitting here,
brother.

12:34.530 --> 12:35.790
Is that right?

12:35.940 --> 12:38.740
Just trying to give you
some friendly advice.

12:38.820 --> 12:40.790
Come with me
or take your chances with them.

12:44.230 --> 12:47.090
- So I should come with you, huh?
- Yeah.

12:48.070 --> 12:51.300
- And not with them?
- Unless you got a loco death wish.

12:51.360 --> 12:55.560
And what if I just wanna
kick it here, keep to myself?

12:55.590 --> 12:58.220
Then I'd imagine
you'd get two shanks in you.

12:58.310 --> 12:59.740
One from each side.

13:07.590 --> 13:10.020
I don't see no shanks in him.

13:10.120 --> 13:13.280
Burke? Don't go near him.

13:13.990 --> 13:16.480
- Why?
- Because he don't want you to.

13:16.580 --> 13:17.640
How you know?

13:17.800 --> 13:20.930
Burke don't give a fuck about
anybody in here but himself.

13:21.540 --> 13:23.070
And that's cool for him.

13:23.210 --> 13:25.370
He can fight his own fights.

13:25.900 --> 13:27.490
But you....

13:28.230 --> 13:30.760
...you wouldn't last a heartbeat.

13:30.860 --> 13:33.720
Come on, I think you gonna
need some friends.

13:34.090 --> 13:36.250
Man, you see these?
I don't need shit.

13:36.460 --> 13:39.720
Put that little motherfucker away.
Let's go see Angel.

13:49.260 --> 13:52.060
Good to meet you.
Name's Angel.

13:52.140 --> 13:54.040
My name's Twitch. What's up?

13:54.280 --> 13:56.270
Right on. Shit.

13:56.400 --> 13:59.520
I'm from L.A. You know, it's a small
little city. You ever heard of it?

13:59.600 --> 14:00.930
I got people in L.A.

14:01.070 --> 14:02.800
I don't.

14:02.920 --> 14:04.910
You a long way from the ocean.

14:05.040 --> 14:07.030
This ain't Malibu.

14:07.150 --> 14:10.210
Every cell is the same to me, man.
Shit, you know- -

14:10.290 --> 14:13.120
Ain't the cells
you got to worry about.

14:13.490 --> 14:16.180
- You know who I am?
- Not really, am I su- -

14:16.270 --> 14:18.430
Wallace tell you nothing about me
when you got here?

14:18.540 --> 14:20.010
Wallace?

14:20.140 --> 14:21.200
That's the warden, right?

14:21.740 --> 14:23.540
Yeah, he like to think so...

14:23.660 --> 14:26.390
...running around here
giving orders with his hard ass.

14:26.480 --> 14:28.470
But in reality...

14:29.100 --> 14:30.970
...I'm the nigga in charge.

14:31.760 --> 14:34.990
I got what you call arrangements.

14:35.470 --> 14:37.200
So you have any problems...

14:37.550 --> 14:39.880
...or need any favors...

14:40.240 --> 14:41.670
...you come see me.

14:42.390 --> 14:43.940
And all I ask in return...

14:45.170 --> 14:48.500
-...is your loyalty.
- Sounds good to me, you know.

14:48.560 --> 14:50.760
- I only- - 
- You got to wear the mark.

14:50.870 --> 14:52.390
Mark?

14:57.110 --> 14:59.040
Angel of Death.

14:59.280 --> 15:00.910
That's what binds us.

15:01.040 --> 15:03.310
Damn. Y'all ain't got
no other type of membership?

15:03.410 --> 15:05.350
You know, like cards or some shit?

15:05.460 --> 15:07.190
Are you in, brother?

15:07.320 --> 15:11.310
Man, I only been here for a day.
Y'all don't even know me.

15:11.350 --> 15:13.010
How you know
I wanna roll with y'all?

15:13.140 --> 15:14.470
Is that a threat?

15:16.980 --> 15:19.680
- Look, man, I'm just saying, man- - 
- Either you with us...

15:19.770 --> 15:21.530
...or you with Cortez.

15:21.650 --> 15:24.450
- I ain't with nobody.
- Listen, brother.

15:24.530 --> 15:25.870
There's a war coming on.

15:26.010 --> 15:28.670
You wear this mark, I guarantee
you won't be a casualty.

15:31.350 --> 15:33.110
Come on.

15:35.260 --> 15:36.450
Move it.

15:36.600 --> 15:40.000
I say we get the brothers together,
man, and make this happen.

15:40.060 --> 15:42.080
- Get up in the line now.
- Get out of my way.

15:42.200 --> 15:45.430
It's just a matter of time before shit
hits the fan with Cortez and his gang.

15:45.500 --> 15:46.830
Be cool, baby, we'll get him.

15:46.970 --> 15:48.940
These motherfuckers.
What are we waiting on?

15:49.050 --> 15:51.520
- We will. We will.
- Come on, when?

15:51.610 --> 15:54.340
When the fuck I say so.

15:54.430 --> 15:58.230
You think you could run this shit
better than me, huh?

15:58.880 --> 16:00.600
Look. What I'm saying is...

16:00.730 --> 16:02.960
...Cortez is bringing in more guards
and more money...

16:03.070 --> 16:05.230
...while you sit around
waiting on God to give you...

16:05.340 --> 16:07.240
-...a motherfucking message.
- Let me ask you- -

16:07.360 --> 16:09.050
What the fuck was that?

16:10.300 --> 16:12.290
You were in my way.

16:13.720 --> 16:15.590
You know something, Burke?

16:15.710 --> 16:19.200
It's about time you fucking learn
how things operate around here.

16:19.260 --> 16:20.790
And you're gonna show me?

16:20.930 --> 16:24.920
Yeah. Go ahead.
I'll let you take the first swing.

16:25.370 --> 16:28.240
Fuck up some of that good behavior
you got going.

16:28.320 --> 16:31.250
- Another time, Angel.
- Don't you walk away from me, Burke.

16:31.330 --> 16:34.130
Don't you fucking walk away
from me, Burke!

16:34.210 --> 16:38.770
One day. You be ready, Burke.
One day.

16:38.780 --> 16:40.620
Dirt nap.

16:40.740 --> 16:42.600
Come on.

16:58.980 --> 17:00.910
We have a deal, right?

17:02.240 --> 17:03.800
Right?

17:05.319 --> 17:07.410
We got the deal.

17:10.819 --> 17:12.450
Okay.

17:59.150 --> 18:01.050
So you Burke, huh?

18:01.480 --> 18:03.250
Ain't that your name?

18:10.640 --> 18:14.130
You know, I heard that you don't
deal with none of the gangs and....

18:14.190 --> 18:15.880
You don't fool with none of that, huh?

18:16.010 --> 18:18.570
Angel's scared of you.

18:18.670 --> 18:22.200
Cortez is afraid of you.

18:22.250 --> 18:24.480
They afraid of me too, you know.

18:24.590 --> 18:27.110
You know, I don't play too much, man.

18:28.970 --> 18:30.670
You a loner, huh?

18:30.800 --> 18:32.530
I'm a loner too,
you know what I'm saying.

18:32.650 --> 18:35.590
Ain't too much I do, you know.
I don't really, you know, get involved- -

18:35.660 --> 18:38.430
Shut up and keep it that way.

18:41.460 --> 18:45.150
- I'm only trying to make it a little easier.
- Don't.

18:50.260 --> 18:53.090
So what you in for anyway, man?
What, you killed somebody?

18:53.170 --> 18:55.540
What, you robbed a bank
or something?

18:55.630 --> 18:58.190
I was thinking about doing
something like that myself, man.

18:58.290 --> 19:02.350
- You could tell me. I'm your boy, man.
- Shut up, will you?

19:02.390 --> 19:04.450
Damn.

19:04.560 --> 19:06.960
Whatever. Shit.

19:10.260 --> 19:13.920
You know, if you don't wanna talk
all you gotta do is just say it.

19:13.970 --> 19:17.460
I'm just trying to communicate
with you, you know.

19:18.360 --> 19:20.480
I don't wanna talk.

19:26.810 --> 19:27.790
That's cool.

19:31.220 --> 19:33.120
Here, sit at number three.

19:33.240 --> 19:34.710
You're not gonna see Dad?

19:34.840 --> 19:37.640
Honey, I have nothing to say
to your dad.

19:39.190 --> 19:40.750
Fine.

19:47.480 --> 19:49.210
It's your time.

19:49.910 --> 19:52.750
Gotta go see my woman, man.
Gonna go do it big.

19:52.830 --> 19:56.190
I'm gonna talk to you later, huh?
Good conversation.

20:00.310 --> 20:02.680
Don't you listen in on my conversation.

20:02.780 --> 20:04.440
Be cool.

20:05.440 --> 20:06.700
Rise, Rise, Rise.

20:06.840 --> 20:10.400
You just had to go and get
your little butt sent to Missouri.

20:10.460 --> 20:12.480
- That's a good thing, ain't it?
- A good thing?

20:12.600 --> 20:15.540
It's harder knowing that you're so close
and I still can't see you.

20:15.610 --> 20:17.010
I know, I know, babe, but look- -

20:17.150 --> 20:20.610
And then it's two more weeks
before I can see your sorry ass again.

20:20.670 --> 20:23.660
- I just can't do it, Bernard.
- What's with all this "Bernard" shit?

20:23.740 --> 20:25.640
I told you,
don't you call me Bernard here.

20:25.760 --> 20:28.190
My name's Twitch. Twitch.

20:28.290 --> 20:30.190
Don't you forget that, woman.

20:30.300 --> 20:33.960
Don't you "woman" me, Bernard.
I put up with enough from you, okay?

20:34.010 --> 20:36.980
I looked the other way
when you had that fat- ass girlfriend.

20:37.050 --> 20:38.580
What was you doing with her anyway?

20:38.720 --> 20:41.210
All she was gonna do was give you
some fat- ass children.

20:41.310 --> 20:44.040
That wasn't fat, that was muscle.

20:44.130 --> 20:47.820
Look, I know, baby, a lot of times
it seems like I take you for granted- -

20:47.870 --> 20:50.000
Oh, you take me for granted
all the time.

20:50.370 --> 20:53.340
I ain't that bad.
I got you the ring, didn't l?

20:53.410 --> 20:55.040
This shit probably ain't even real.

20:55.170 --> 20:57.330
I don't know when you plan
on having the wedding...

20:57.440 --> 20:59.170
...but I am calling it off.

20:59.300 --> 21:01.270
Yes, I'm calling it off, okay?

21:01.380 --> 21:02.870
Your momma gonna be so upset.

21:03.010 --> 21:05.640
Wait, wait, hold on, hold on, baby.
Hold on, now.

21:06.370 --> 21:07.800
I know I make a lot of promises.

21:07.940 --> 21:10.770
Yeah. You make a lot of promises,
like you gonna marry me...

21:10.850 --> 21:13.320
...Iike you love me,
like you gonna get parole.

21:13.410 --> 21:16.070
- But- - 
- You never deliver on the promises.

21:16.160 --> 21:18.390
Ever. How am I supposed to trust you?

21:18.500 --> 21:20.900
First of all, I am getting parole, Cherise.

21:21.000 --> 21:22.930
- When?
- Soon.

21:25.760 --> 21:27.490
Hello, Amy.

21:31.010 --> 21:32.780
Hey, Ellie.

21:33.060 --> 21:34.930
You look great.

21:35.270 --> 21:36.700
You changed your hair, didn't you?

21:36.840 --> 21:39.270
- I like it.
- Thanks.

21:39.370 --> 21:41.840
- How's school, baby?
- It's summer.

21:42.600 --> 21:45.160
Oh, sorry.

21:46.210 --> 21:50.050
- No, this is it, Bernard. I'm leaving.
- Wait, wait, hold on.

21:51.310 --> 21:52.770
All right, now.

21:52.900 --> 21:56.000
I gotta tell you something.
I am getting out, okay?

21:56.070 --> 21:58.040
- I just- - 
- Forget you, Bernard.

21:58.150 --> 22:01.520
Just listen to me, okay?
Damn.

22:01.580 --> 22:03.740
What I'm talking about
has to do with our future.

22:03.850 --> 22:07.080
Okay. All right. You know,
this better be real good.

22:07.150 --> 22:09.270
It is good. Now, I got a plan.

22:09.390 --> 22:12.450
- A plan?
- Yeah, a plan.

22:12.710 --> 22:13.870
It's gonna get us rich.

22:14.030 --> 22:16.520
What the hell are you thinking?
You gonna get rich in here?

22:16.620 --> 22:18.140
You sound like some kind of fool.

22:18.280 --> 22:21.740
Who are you talking to?
Now, just listen to me.

22:21.800 --> 22:24.400
Me getting transferred here
was a part of the plan.

22:24.490 --> 22:26.390
- What you mean?
- I mean...

22:26.510 --> 22:28.370
...I got transferred here
on purpose.

22:28.490 --> 22:30.360
Now I know you's a fool.

22:30.480 --> 22:34.210
