some officer fatalities.

45:22.000 --> 45:25.400
Damn it, Wallace. I mean, it's the last
thing we need in an election year.

45:25.810 --> 45:29.340
- How many officers?
- Three that we know of for sure.

45:29.390 --> 45:33.590
All right. Look, you need to end this
thing quickly, no matter what it takes.

45:33.620 --> 45:36.550
All right?
But protect our people at all cost.

45:36.630 --> 45:37.850
Has the press been notified?

45:38.000 --> 45:40.340
No, sir. We've been able
to keep a lid on that.

45:40.630 --> 45:45.120
All right. My office will handle
all the press from this end.

45:45.140 --> 45:47.610
Just a minute. Charlie.
Hey, call the airport...

45:47.700 --> 45:50.670
...make sure the helicopter's ready,
wheels up in 20 minutes.

45:50.740 --> 45:52.640
We're going to Creighton.

45:52.760 --> 45:53.720
I'm on my way.

45:53.880 --> 45:55.470
Yes, sir.

46:02.290 --> 46:05.020
- Here we go.
- Tell me why you got transferred here.

46:05.460 --> 46:07.520
- Tell me.
- What, you don't know?

46:07.640 --> 46:10.300
- Bullshit about a fight.
- It was more than a fight.

46:10.390 --> 46:12.830
It's three of them and they thought
because I'm little...

46:12.950 --> 46:16.010
...I couldn't whoop that ass,
but I got this thing I did:

46:17.910 --> 46:19.970
- You can't fight worth a shit.
- Shut up.

46:20.090 --> 46:21.720
Kick your ass.

46:21.850 --> 46:24.320
- What?
- If my ankle didn't hurt.

46:24.860 --> 46:28.690
Hey, quit lying to me.
Why'd you get transferred here?

46:28.730 --> 46:33.290
I- -  I wanted to be closer
to my fiancee, Cherise.

46:33.310 --> 46:35.600
- You're lying.
- No, I'm not.

46:35.710 --> 46:36.760
Your eyes are moving...

46:36.920 --> 46:38.910
-...and you're lying.
- My eyes always move.

46:39.030 --> 46:42.700
Yeah, that's my point exactly.
Why'd you get transferred here?

46:42.750 --> 46:44.440
Look, I can't swim.

46:44.860 --> 46:47.890
Creighton has no water or sharks.

46:47.960 --> 46:52.700
You're telling me you got transferred
here just so you could escape?

46:52.700 --> 46:56.500
Goddamn right.
I'm a crazy motherfucker.

46:58.970 --> 47:00.000
No shit.

47:02.400 --> 47:04.990
There's the motherfucker
that killed Angel.

47:06.170 --> 47:08.140
Hey, hey, hey. Wait, wait, wait!

47:19.940 --> 47:21.630
- Come on.
- Bitch!

47:23.070 --> 47:24.800
Any luck?

47:24.930 --> 47:26.730
It's not working.

47:27.040 --> 47:29.270
Just keep trying.

47:29.790 --> 47:31.420
Been trying.

47:32.550 --> 47:34.170
Look, we need another way.

47:34.310 --> 47:37.000
God knows when that guy
is gonna come back.

47:41.320 --> 47:43.180
This is creepy.

47:44.070 --> 47:45.900
It's where people watch
the executions.

47:46.020 --> 47:47.490
Yeah.

47:47.620 --> 47:50.350
- I could never do it.
- Do what?

47:50.630 --> 47:53.290
Just sit there and watch people die.

47:56.740 --> 47:59.210
We gotta get this door open.
It's our only way out.

48:14.890 --> 48:16.910
You tried to get out?

48:17.420 --> 48:20.320
After what we just said to you?

48:26.250 --> 48:27.980
Tie her up.

48:29.320 --> 48:31.190
What the hell is wrong with you?

48:32.940 --> 48:37.070
I said, tie her up.

48:53.680 --> 48:56.080
It's too much like Alcatraz.

48:56.620 --> 48:59.180
Eric, make sure each officer gets one.

48:59.280 --> 49:02.540
Robert, back to the office
and monitor everything from there.

49:02.600 --> 49:05.770
All right, everybody. Time to move.

49:07.820 --> 49:10.950
All officers,
this is the warden speaking.

49:11.020 --> 49:14.360
Take back control
one cellblock at a time.

49:14.410 --> 49:16.850
There's some inmates
to be on the lookout for.

49:16.940 --> 49:20.740
One William Burke.
One Bernard "Twitch" Washington.

49:20.780 --> 49:22.940
Both suspects
in the murder of two guards.

49:23.060 --> 49:24.280
Did he just say my name?

49:25.070 --> 49:27.270
Twitch is the transfer
from New Alcatraz.

49:27.380 --> 49:29.500
Both he and Burke
are likely armed.

49:29.620 --> 49:31.450
No, no, we ain't, man.
Tell him we're not.

49:31.570 --> 49:33.470
Try to take them alive.

49:33.590 --> 49:35.520
- Shoot to kill if you have to.
- Give me that.

49:35.630 --> 49:39.160
- Man, you ain't talking to him.
- Look, I've gotta clear my name, Burke.

49:39.920 --> 49:42.360
We've got another situation
we gotta handle.

49:42.450 --> 49:46.320
Another inmate, Alex Cortez,
has taken hostages inside.

49:46.350 --> 49:47.750
We don't know exactly
how many...

49:47.890 --> 49:51.190
...but we believe
there are two missing visitors.

49:51.250 --> 49:53.840
- One Cherise- - 
- Hey, man, give me this thing.

49:53.940 --> 49:55.100
Wallace.

49:55.250 --> 49:56.840
- You there?
- Who's this?

49:56.980 --> 49:58.380
This is Twitch, man.

49:58.520 --> 50:00.510
Just what the hell
do you think you're doing?

50:00.630 --> 50:04.930
Hey, man, why you got this APB
out on me, man? I ain't kill nobody.

50:04.950 --> 50:06.610
No one's accused you of anything.

50:07.030 --> 50:09.500
Yeah, you did. You got the APB
cracking on us, man.

50:09.910 --> 50:12.380
Rioters everywhere, man.
That's not due process.

50:12.470 --> 50:15.910
Okay, then turn yourself in
and let's clear this up.

50:17.560 --> 50:19.580
- What? What is it?
- We're not meeting him.

50:19.700 --> 50:22.800
- Twitch, are you there?
- Yeah, man.

50:22.870 --> 50:25.400
Well, what do you say?
About going over this face to face?

50:26.840 --> 50:28.030
I know how that one works.

50:28.180 --> 50:30.240
We get there
and all your guard dogs are there.

50:30.360 --> 50:32.160
You can forget that one, buddy.

50:32.280 --> 50:34.340
My men won't harm you, I promise.

50:35.260 --> 50:37.660
Man, you gonna call the APB off
or what, Wallace?

50:37.750 --> 50:40.120
Just tell me where you are
and we'll work this- -

50:40.220 --> 50:41.810
You're not gonna meet with him.

50:41.980 --> 50:44.570
Man, this is bullshit.
This prison's full of shit.

50:46.040 --> 50:47.010
Twitch?

50:51.640 --> 50:55.240
Twitch. Goddamn it, let's go.

50:55.290 --> 50:57.050
Open it.

51:03.550 --> 51:08.920
The second hostage is Ellie Burke,
daughter of inmate William Burke.

51:15.740 --> 51:19.300
Keep your eyes right. Move it out.
Keep your eyes right. Move it.

51:29.920 --> 51:32.080
Hey, perro. Look at this.
Handle it.

51:32.190 --> 51:34.090
Hurry up, men. Hurry up.

51:38.720 --> 51:40.210
Where's Burke?

51:40.350 --> 51:41.820
I don't know.

51:42.690 --> 51:45.820
- Are you sure?
- I don't give a damn about Burke.

51:45.890 --> 51:48.920
- You, motherfu- - 
- Wow, easy, easy. Easy.

51:51.330 --> 51:52.660
Is that right?

51:52.800 --> 51:53.900
Where's your jefe?

51:54.150 --> 51:55.810
I don't give a damn about him, either.

51:55.940 --> 51:58.600
You see, because he fucked me over
with his escape plan, man.

51:59.360 --> 52:01.990
- Escape plan?
- That's right. He took hostages.

52:02.080 --> 52:04.880
And, you know,
one of them is Burke's daughter.

52:04.960 --> 52:08.830
That's right. Yeah. And he's going
to use them to get out of here.

52:08.870 --> 52:11.000
Bet you didn't know that, huh?

52:12.520 --> 52:14.610
Hey, perro, that's the police
with riot gear.

52:14.730 --> 52:16.250
- Stop!
- This don't look good, man.

52:16.390 --> 52:18.620
Show these motherfuckers
who run this place!

53:25.770 --> 53:27.400
Tear gas.

53:29.900 --> 53:31.270
Get out of here.

53:53.780 --> 53:55.940
Keep going, man. What?

54:01.650 --> 54:04.240
- Let's move it, dog. Let's move.
- Fuck you.

54:11.540 --> 54:13.200
I don't like the way this shit sounds.

54:13.330 --> 54:16.030
It don't sound like they're handling
this too good, man.

54:16.120 --> 54:18.020
Cortez ain't gonna surrender, man.

54:18.130 --> 54:20.930
- We gotta get to him first.
- Look, I've been here before.

54:21.010 --> 54:22.240
Nobody wins.

54:22.900 --> 54:24.530
What are you talking about?

54:24.660 --> 54:25.720
The Rock.

54:26.140 --> 54:29.630
New Alcatraz.
Man, I did five years, man.

54:29.690 --> 54:32.660
One night, man,
it was just raining like fuck, man.

54:32.730 --> 54:35.090
Fucking helicopter crashed
into the roof, man.

54:38.710 --> 54:40.270
No!

54:58.070 --> 55:01.200
People started coming out, man,
shooting people with all kinds of guns.

55:16.730 --> 55:20.790
Inmates died, guards died, you know.
A lot of shit was going on, man.

55:20.830 --> 55:23.760
Come on, I lost a lot of people
in there, man.

55:23.840 --> 55:25.070
People that I cared about.

55:27.360 --> 55:28.620
No!

55:29.410 --> 55:31.030
No! No!

55:35.900 --> 55:37.430
God.

55:41.730 --> 55:44.820
Why the hell would guys
break into prison?

55:45.630 --> 55:47.930
Man, none of that matters to me.
Just listen to me.

55:48.030 --> 55:50.730
A lot of shit happened, okay?

55:50.820 --> 55:54.880
- I ain't trying to go through shit again.
- Look, man, this time's different.

55:54.910 --> 55:56.570
Follow me.

56:00.000 --> 56:01.900
How we gonna- -? Damn....

56:02.020 --> 56:05.040
Look, I could teach you some shit.
Man, I should just- -

56:05.120 --> 56:07.490
- Hey, no.
- Big bad Burke.

56:09.000 --> 56:13.090
Yeah, you couldn't do it like a man.
You had to do it like a little bitch.

56:13.120 --> 56:15.420
- It's not what you think.
- You know what I'm thinking?

56:15.520 --> 56:17.010
Yeah, I didn't kill Angel.

56:17.380 --> 56:19.180
Oh, so you still can't admit that shit?

56:19.300 --> 56:21.530
I'd respect you more
if you could admit that shit.

56:21.640 --> 56:23.370
So we gonna do this like men.

56:23.490 --> 56:25.020
Old- school style.

56:25.350 --> 56:26.540
Do what you gotta do.

56:55.210 --> 56:57.840
Now, see, that was just the appetizer.

56:57.930 --> 56:59.330
Now it's time for the main course.

56:59.470 --> 57:02.160
We're gonna cut your ass up,
make you into some Chinese food...

57:02.250 --> 57:04.310
...and serve you to the skinheads.

57:05.190 --> 57:07.960
Look at me. Yeah.

57:08.590 --> 57:10.580
Old- school style.

57:14.320 --> 57:16.180
Take this motherfucker
to the cafeteria.

57:16.300 --> 57:17.890
Yeah.

57:30.290 --> 57:32.690
Get that fryer going. Get it going.

57:34.190 --> 57:35.890
Yeah, yeah. This will do.

57:38.130 --> 57:41.030
This is what we're gonna do.
What it look like?

57:41.100 --> 57:43.590
Looks like you gonna
cook something.

57:44.110 --> 57:46.840
Cortez killed Angel, not me.

57:47.920 --> 57:49.890
- Oh, fuck, man.
- Let him go.

57:50.000 --> 57:52.400
- Easy, easy, cool. Let him go.
- I'll whoop your ass.

57:52.500 --> 57:53.460
Easy.

57:53.620 --> 57:55.680
Come on, JT, listen to me.
Listen to me.

57:56.530 --> 58:00.120
I ain't gonna say nothing to nobody,
you already know that.

58:00.180 --> 58:02.740
What about the rest
of these motherfuckers, shit?

58:02.830 --> 58:05.600
Is everybody else gonna be quiet
about the whole thing?

58:05.680 --> 58:08.080
- What the hell is you saying, Twitch?
- I'm just saying...

58:08.180 --> 58:10.170
...we gonna kill this motherfucker,
right?

58:10.290 --> 58:13.450
I mean, what, is everybody else
gonna be quiet about the whole thing?

58:13.940 --> 58:17.000
- Damn right.
- And take it to their grave?

58:19.250 --> 58:21.220
I mean, fuck it, cook him.

58:21.330 --> 58:23.930
If anybody gonna speak
a word about this, it's you.

58:24.150 --> 58:27.020
Snitch.
Now get the fuck out the way.

58:27.090 --> 58:29.530
Fellas, we gonna have
"sum dumb fuck" on the menu.

58:29.620 --> 58:32.520
- Shit. Quit pushing.
- It's too bad, Burke.

58:32.600 --> 58:35.230
You won't get a chance
to save your daughter.

58:35.320 --> 58:37.480
Oh, you didn't know, did you?

58:38.100 --> 58:41.770
This motherfucker didn't know
Cortez had his daughter as hostage.

58:41.810 --> 58:44.610
It's a first- class ticket
out of motherfucking paradise.

59:01.430 --> 59:04.330
Yeah, and after Cortez,
I got next, motherfucker.

59:17.050 --> 59:19.710
Come here, come on, Burke.
Burke, Burke, Burke, come on.

59:19.800 --> 59:22.530
We gotta go. We gotta go.

59:46.140 --> 59:48.630
- I don't like the sound of this.
- I'm going after Cortez.

59:48.740 --> 59:50.970
- You going after him?
- He's got my daughter.

59:51.070 --> 59:54.040
You wanna escape? Go ahead.

59:54.560 --> 59:56.290
You tripping.

01:00:02.020 --> 01:00:03.950
Hey, Burke. Hold on, man.

01:00:04.450 --> 01:00:06.850
Wallace, is the governor on his way?

01:00:07.520 --> 01:00:09.620
What do you want with him?

01:00:18.630 --> 01:00:21.390
This is the governor. I'm on my way.
ETA 30 minutes.

01:00:21.480 --> 01:00:23.770
I want the whole prison locked down
by the time I get there.

01:00:24.160 --> 01:00:26.430
Now, we've got another situation
we've gotta handle.

01:00:26.530 --> 01:00:30.130
Two guards are confirmed dead.
We have suspects.

01:00:30.180 --> 01:00:32.550
Our men are tracking them now.

01:00:32.650 --> 01:00:35.440
I want those guys caught.
Dead or alive.

01:00:35.530 --> 01:00:36.620
Doesn't matter to me.

01:00:37.250 --> 01:00:39.850
Make sure you keep the situation
under control.

01:00:39.940 --> 01:00:42.210
I'll be there as soon as I can.

01:00:46.050 --> 01:00:48.920
Wait, wait. Hold on, Burke.

01:00:49.000 --> 01:00:51.160
- Hold on. Damn.
- Shit.

01:00:51.270 --> 01:00:54.140
- Come on, give me a hand.
- Wait, wait, wait. Let me try this.

01:00:54.220 --> 01:00:55.650
Pull.

01:00:55.780 --> 01:00:57.780
- Just....
- Over here, hermano.

01:00:58.540 --> 01:01:00.260
Come on.

01:01:00.390 --> 01:01:02.490
- Come on.
- I can't.

01:01:02.600 --> 01:01:05.630
- Wait. I got an idea, I got an idea.
- What?

01:01:06.310 --> 01:01:07.970
Well, you know...

01:01:08.110 --> 01:01:10.800
...I used to steal cars.
I could hot- wire this bitch.

01:01:10.890 --> 01:01:12.220
Man, hurry up, will you?

01:01:14.190 --> 01:01:16.450
So tell me your charge.

01:01:16.550 --> 01:01:19.790
- I'll tell you mine.
- I don't really care.

01:01:19.850 --> 01:01:22.150
Breaking and entering, huh?

01:01:22.920 --> 01:01:26.120
- What, you hit the White House?
- Man, hurry up!

01:01:26.190 --> 01:01:27.590
I'm not doing shit.

01:01:30.670 --> 01:01:32.730
What you in here for?

01:01:33.960 --> 01:01:37.460
- I'm in here for nothing.
- Man, that's what they all say, man.

01:01:38.730 --> 01:01:42.100
Okay, a friend of mine knocked off
an armored car.

01:01:42.160 --> 01:01:44.150
I should have known about it,
but I didn't.

01:01:44.270 --> 01:01:46.530
Cops found him at my house
with a bag full of cash.

01:01:46.670 --> 01:01:48.760
- Bag full of cash?
- Yeah.

01:01:48.880 --> 01:01:53.040
He implicated me, knocked
a couple of years off his sentence.

01:01:53.810 --> 01:01:56.240
I got five years.

01:01:56.660 --> 01:01:58.380
I lost my wife.

01:01:58.510 --> 01:02:01.410
She took my little girl away from me.

01:02:01.490 --> 01:02:03.250
She's the only thing I ever loved.

01:02:04.270 --> 01:02:06.330
Everybody else....

01:02:06.450 --> 01:02:09.080
Everybody else has shit on me.

01:02:09.590 --> 01:02:11.920
I got burnt before too, Burke.

01:02:14.160 --> 01:02:15.990
I'd never burn you, homey.

01:02:16.370 --> 01:02:17.600
Yeah, we'll see.

01:02:19.600 --> 01:02:22.230
- Get that motherfucker. Come on.
- Oh, shit.

01:02:33.400 --> 01:02:35.090
Come on, Burke.

01:02:40.340 --> 01:02:43.140
Fuck you, Burke. You're a dead man.

01:02:43.800 --> 01:02:46.030
- Yo, dog, this way.
- All right, all right.

01:02:48.410 --> 01:02:49.900
Ready?

01:02:50.580 --> 01:02:53.710
- Let's go, let's go.
- Let's go. Move it out.

01:02:55.580 --> 01:02:57.410
Total lockdown.

01:02:58.680 --> 01:03:01.310
Let's put this all back together, now.

01:03:06.970 --> 01:03:08.530
Get ready for anything.

01:03:09.820 --> 01:03:12.980
Half the cellblocks are under control.
It's a matter of time for the rest.

01:03:13.050 --> 01:03:16.850
Still no Cortez. This is a prison.
How many places can he hide?

01:03:16.890 --> 01:03:18.520
How does he think he's gonna get out?

01:03:39.640 --> 01:03:41.740
- Glad you could make it, sir.
- What's the status?

01:03:41.850 --> 01:03:43.250
Afraid things have gotten worse.

01:03:43.390 --> 01:03:47.050
Inmate Alex Cortez has captured
two civilian hostages.

01:03:47.100 --> 01:03:49.000
- Both females.
- Christ.

01:03:49.120 --> 01:03:50.920
Wallace, how could this happen?

01:03:51.040 --> 01:03:53.530
Governor, the riot began
just after visitation...

01:03:53.630 --> 01:03:56.330
...and one of the hostages
was in the conjugal room.

01:03:56.410 --> 01:03:59.910
All right, let's get in there.
I wanna talk to this Cortez.

01:04:08.480 --> 01:04:10.210
Burke locked us up.
He's a dead man.

01:04:10.340 --> 01:04:14.500
Hey, you do this thing,
you're gonna get out of here. Soon.

01:04:14.530 --> 01:04:16.050
Got it?

01:04:19.270 --> 01:04:22.060
This place is falling apart, man.

01:04:22.310 --> 01:04:25.760
- Oh, shit.
- Burke, I've been looking for you.

01:04:26.180 --> 01:04:27.540
Check it out, man.

01:04:27.680 --> 01:04:28.650
Where's Cortez?

01:04:28.800 --> 01:04:31.740
You just follow me. I know
where that motherfucker Cortez is, bro.

01:04:31.810 --> 01:04:33.300
- Come on.
- I don't like this.

01:04:33.440 --> 01:04:35.280
This runs below the cellblock.

01:04:35.400 --> 01:04:37.890
- It ends at the machine shop.
- That's where Cortez is?

01:04:37.990 --> 01:04:41.220
That's right, the motherfucker.
He knew about this shit all along.

01:04:41.280 --> 01:04:43.180
Just around here.

01:04:43.720 --> 01:04:45.270
Shit.

01:04:45.610 --> 01:04:49.800
- Where are you leading us, man?
- I told you, Cortez. Relax, man.

01:04:50.890 --> 01:04:52.410
Why are you telling us this?

01:04:52.550 --> 01:04:56.010
I was supposed to break out with this
motherfucking bitch. He betrayed me.

01:04:56.070 --> 01:04:58.440
And I want some
motherfucking payback.

01:04:58.530 --> 01:04:59.830
I could use your help.

01:05:00.360 --> 01:05:03.330
Listen, I don't give a shit
about payback.

01:05:03.400 --> 01:05:05.530
I just wanna find my daughter.

01:05:07.980 --> 01:05:09.570
Man, I don't like this.

01:05:09.740 --> 01:05:12.140
I don't like this. How come
nobody else know about this?

01:05:12.230 --> 01:05:14.560
A cop will sell any information
for a price.

01:05:15.050 --> 01:05:16.480
Hey!

01:05:17.100 --> 01:05:19.960
Rivera! Fuck.

01:05:21.070 --> 01:05:24.970
What the fuck? I knew we
couldn't trust this fucking guy.

01:05:27.080 --> 01:05:31.640
You know what? You tell the warden
when this is all over, he'll pay.

01:05:31.660 --> 01:05:35.290
When I get my hands on Cortez,
I'm gonna snap his fucking neck.

01:05:38.090 --> 01:05:39.960
Gotta be another way.

01:06:06.220 --> 01:06:07.190
Oh, shit.

01:07:06.840 --> 01:07:08.500
I didn't do nothing.

01:07:09.340 --> 01:07:11.330
- Let's go, come on.
- Twitch.

01:07:16.150 --> 01:07:17.240
Better come.

01:07:44.640 --> 01:07:46.540
Look, I want some answers
and I want them now.

01:07:46.650 --> 01:07:48.280
And this time, I want the truth.

